@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nmekbl(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.sin(0.46) / (wp.cos(v1 + 0.18) * wp.sin(v2 + 0.85)))
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.sin(v2 + 0.39) / (v1 + 0.45 / tmp + 0.89)))
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.21)) / (v1 / (tmp + 0.05 * v0 + 0.57)))
    v2 = 0.99
    tmp = wp.abs(((v1 + 0.21 / tmp + 0.96) / (v1 + 0.80 * v0 + 0.07)))
    data[tid] = v0
